    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR3l0099-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_000-1a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">and without blame.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_000-2a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">Compiled by Gan Bao of Xincai, Attendant Gentleman of the Jin Dynasty, under the order of Ling Sheng.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-h" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">Volume 1</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-1a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">Shennong used a red whip to whip the hundred herbs,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">fully knowing their properties of neutrality, toxicity, coldness, and warmth,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">and what their smells and tastes were good for,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">in order to sow the hundred grains.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">Therefore, the world called him Shennong.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-2a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">Chi Songzi (Master Red Pine) was</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">the rain master during the time of Shennong.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">He took Bingyu Powder (Ice Jade Powder)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">and taught it to Shennong.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">He could enter fire without being burned.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-2a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">He went to Kunlun Mountain,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-2a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">and often entered the stone chamber of the Queen Mother of the West,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-2a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">ascending and descending with the wind and rain.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-2a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">A young daughter of Emperor Yan pursued him,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-2a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">also attained immortality,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-2a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">and they both left.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-2a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">During the time of Emperor Gao Xin,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-2a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">he again served as rain master,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-2a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">traveling among men.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-2a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">The present-day rain master is originally from him.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-3a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">Chi Jiangzi Yu (Master Red General Yu) was</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">a man of the time of the Yellow Emperor.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">He did not eat the five grains,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">but ate the flowers of the hundred herbs.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">By the time of Emperor Yao,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:24:14.304+09:00">he was a carpenter.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">He could rise and fall with the wind and rain.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-3a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">He sometimes sold stringed arrows in the marketplace,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-3a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">so he was also called "Stringed Arrow Father."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-4a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">Ning Fengzi</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-4a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">was a man of the time of the Yellow Emperor.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-4a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">Tradition says he was the potter for the Yellow Emperor.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-4a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">A strange man passed by him</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-4a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">and was hired to manage the fire.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-4a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">He could produce smoke of five colors.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-4a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">After a long time, he taught Fengzi this skill.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-4a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">Fengzi accumulated fire and burned himself,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-4a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">and rose and fell with the smoke.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-4a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">Examining his ashes,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-4a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">there were still bones.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-4a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">The people of that time buried him together in the northern mountains of Ning.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-4a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">Therefore, he was called Ning Fengzi.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-5a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">Wo Quan</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-5a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">was a medicine-gathering father from Huai Mountain.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-5a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">He liked to eat pine nuts.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-5a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">His body grew hair,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-5a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">and he was seven inches tall.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-5a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">His eyes were square.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-5a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">He could fly and chase running horses.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-5a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">He gave pine nuts to Yao,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-5a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">but Yao did not have time to eat them.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-5a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">The pine nuts</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-5a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">were from the Jian pine.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-5a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">Those who took them</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-5a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">all lived three hundred years.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-6a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">Peng Zu</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-6a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">was a minister during the Yin dynasty.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-6a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-08T09:25:34.624+09:00">His surname was Qian</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-6a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">His name was Keng.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-6a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">He was the grandson of Emperor Zhuanxu,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">"That is not a ghost."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">Ding Bo said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">"I am a new ghost,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">so my body is heavy."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">Thereupon Ding Bo carried the ghost again,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">and the ghost felt barely any weight.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">This happened again and again.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">Ding Bo again said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">"I am a new ghost,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">and do not know what things are to be feared or avoided."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">The ghost answered,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">"We only dislike people spitting."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">Thereupon they continued traveling together.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">On the road they encountered water.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">Ding Bo ordered the ghost to cross first.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">He listened to it,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">and heard no sound at all.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">Ding Bo crossed himself,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">making a "splash-splash" sound.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">The ghost again said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">"Why is there a sound?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">Ding Bo said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">"I am newly dead,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.53" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">and not yet accustomed to crossing water.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.54" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">Do not be surprised at me."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.55" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">As they were about to reach Wan City market,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.56" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">Ding Bo then carried the ghost,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.57" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">putting it on his shoulder,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.58" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">and quickly seized it.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.59" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">The ghost shouted loudly,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.60" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">its voice "tsk-tsk",</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.61" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">demanding to be put down,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.62" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">but he no longer listened to it.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_016-18a.63" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T01:16:31.363+09:00">He went directly to the middle of Wan City market and put it down on the ground.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-6a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">the second son of Lu Zhong.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-6a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">He lived from the Xia dynasty to the end of the Shang dynasty,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-6a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">and was said to have lived seven hundred years.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-6a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">He often ate cassia bark and mushrooms.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-6a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">In Liyang, there is the immortal chamber of Peng Zu.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-6a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">It is said by past generations that</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-6a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">if one prayed for wind and rain,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-6a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">the request would always be answered.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-6a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">There were often two tigers on the left and right of the shrine.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-6a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">After worshipping at the shrine today,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-6a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">there would be two tiger tracks on the ground.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-7a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-05-09T10:39:50.085+09:00">Shimen</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-7a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">was a disciple of Xiaofu.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-7a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">He could control fire.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-7a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">He ate peach blossoms.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-7a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">He became Kong Jia's dragon master.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-7a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">Kong Jia could not understand his intentions,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-7a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">so he killed him and buried him in the wilderness.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-7a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-05-09T10:40:38.154+09:00">One day at dawn,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-7a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">wind and rain welcomed him.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-7a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">All the trees in the mountains were burned.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-7a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">Kong Jia built a shrine and prayed to him,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-7a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">but he died before he could return.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-8a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">Ge You of the former Zhou dynasty</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-8a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">was a Qiang person from Shu.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-8a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">During the time of King Cheng of Zhou,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-8a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">he liked to carve wooden sheep and sell them.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-8a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">One day,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-8a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">he rode a wooden sheep into Shu.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-8a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">The kings, nobles, and dignitaries of Shu chased him</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-8a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">up Mount Sui.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3l0099_tls_001-8a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-09T10:38:52.884+09:00">Mount Sui has many peaches.</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
